## 1. Purpose
This protocol defines the mandatory process for verifying implemented functionality, starting automatically when the agent deems development complete, and requiring explicit user interaction to begin active testing and final approval before a task can be marked as fully completed (`âœ…`). It ensures quality control and alignment with user expectations.

